          "action": "escalate_to_human",
          "handoffTarget": "SIU compliance manager (DOI fraud bureau liaison)",
          "rationale": "Statutory fraud reports have fixed deadlines and prescribed forms (e.g., FD-1/eFD), and late or defective filings expose the carrier to administrative penalties."
        }
